DeVry University Pomona
Automated Delivery System

The Automated Delivery System (ADS) will be used as a delivery system within a building or area and will follow a path specified by the user.  It will be able to carry small packages, parts, mail, whatever need be. This can also be useful in saving time and man hours in situations such as time spent going back and forth for parts, supplies, mail, and ensures maximum time spent on the task at hand. Its purpose is to decrease man hours spent on menial delivery tasks.
